arStrings.szText: Donan has asked for my help attuning the Soulstone to Mephisto's essence. We are to meet outside the ruin of a Zakarum fortress deep in the swamps of Hawezar.

Donan and I have entered the ruined Zakarum fortress in Hawezar and must explore the Foul Crypt beneath it for the Black Tomb of Sankekur. Only there can we find a suitable place to attune the Soulstone.
